node.text:
This WEEK be determined to MOVE UP and FORWARD! How do you do that? Release yourself from ALL shame, pain and stress! You got this!! Let’s go! This week is your week for breakthroughs! Brethren, I count not myself to have apprehended: but this one thing I do, forgetting those things which are behind, and reaching forth unto those things which are before, 14. I press toward the mark for the prize of the high calling of God in Christ Jesus. 
Phil 3:13-14

node.text: This will be an extraordinary week. Prayers will be answered back to back. Believe that!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by REAL TALK KIM on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I Made Some Mistakes I Cant Change, But I Changed So I Wont Make The Same Mistakes!!'.

node.text: Stop living in shame and forgive yourself and let it go! If you erased all your mistakes you wouldn’t be the amazing human you are today! Life is about change! God has You! Grow through what you’re going through! Cheers to a better Us!

node.text: MARRY someone who will not only accept the call of God on your life, but will also help you fulfill it and not try to kill it. The wrong person can delay your destiny! Listen, nothing worse than marrying Satan and having to pretend you are happy! Stop that!! Wait on God! #single #relationship #dating

node.text:
Good Mornin Family!! 
Today I decree that you experience restoration from the years the locusts and cankerworm have eaten. I decree everything that has seemed to have decayed or crumbled be reestablished into newness and may you begin to flourish again. I prophesy a rebuilding of the old waste places and that streams begin to flow in the desert. I break the power of distraction, attack, and devastation in Jesus name. I pray that you begin to receive restitution, payback, benefits, and reimbursements. 
I pray that fruitfulness will remain in your life and that you will experience fulfillment, success, and complete contentment. I prophecy that all that God has planned for your life will begin to fully manifest in this season before you! I speak all of this in Jesus name. #realtalk #realtalkkim
